WEBVTT

00:17.000 --> 00:19.600
SUI

00:19.680 --> 00:20.640
XIE

00:20.720 --> 00:21.960
All soldiers, hear my command.

00:22.960 --> 00:25.480
Bring me Prince Changxin's head.

00:25.560 --> 00:28.160
Charge!

00:28.240 --> 00:29.680
Kill!

00:29.760 --> 00:36.520
Kill!

00:47.080 --> 00:48.040
Charge!

00:48.120 --> 00:50.920
Kill!

01:01.560 --> 01:02.560
Commander Li.

01:18.920 --> 01:20.320
All soldiers, hear my command.

01:22.720 --> 01:24.920
Prince Changxin's main force
has begun the assault on the city.

01:25.000 --> 01:26.800
You must follow me.

01:26.880 --> 01:28.440
We strike directly at the rear
of the Chongzhou army.

01:28.520 --> 01:29.840
We take out the Prince directly!

01:29.920 --> 01:31.200
-Yes!
-Yes!

01:31.280 --> 01:34.000
Commander Li, wounded as you are,
don't fight them head-on.

01:34.600 --> 01:36.360
Leave this to us. We'll handle it.

01:39.920 --> 01:41.680
If this life of mine can save more people,

01:43.320 --> 01:44.960
then dying would be worth it.

01:50.000 --> 01:51.000
Mr. Jin.

01:54.040 --> 01:55.720
You… Lord!

01:57.560 --> 01:58.880
Commander Zhuo,

01:58.960 --> 02:01.160
take him somewhere safe
and take good care of him.

02:01.240 --> 02:03.040
Taking out the rebel headquarters,

02:03.120 --> 02:03.960
we'll handle that.

02:05.480 --> 02:07.640
Mrs. Fan, we'll go with you.

02:08.160 --> 02:10.160
-We'll go with you.
-We'll go with you.

02:10.240 --> 02:13.080
We'll go with you.

03:43.360 --> 03:48.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

04:58.600 --> 05:01.360
He Jingyuan's army. Why are they here?

05:02.160 --> 05:04.080
Stop them. Don't let them
disrupt our formation.

05:04.160 --> 05:05.120
-Yes, sir.
-Follow me!

05:06.040 --> 05:07.280
Move.

05:22.760 --> 05:23.920
Report from the front.

05:24.000 --> 05:26.040
We've made it onto the city wall,
but casualties are heavy.

05:26.120 --> 05:27.240
We need reinforcements urgently.

05:27.320 --> 05:28.840
Good. Go at once.

05:58.680 --> 05:59.920
Yan Zheng.

06:11.040 --> 06:11.880
I knew you'd come.

06:11.960 --> 06:13.600
Stay behind me. Keep close.

06:18.160 --> 06:19.560
I'm not hiding behind anyone.

06:20.720 --> 06:22.680
Prince Changxin,
Sui Yuanqing, take your pick.

06:27.920 --> 06:29.560
I'll take Prince Changxin. You be careful.

06:55.000 --> 06:56.880
‎HE

07:39.840 --> 07:40.920
Big brother!

07:54.560 --> 07:56.040
Then die together.

08:04.680 --> 08:06.240
Man Di!

08:08.440 --> 08:10.400
Sui Yuanqing! I'll kill you!

08:16.280 --> 08:17.520
-Little brother…
-Man Di.

08:17.600 --> 08:19.520
-Man Di.
-Man Di.

08:20.480 --> 08:21.240
-Man Di.
-Man Di.

08:21.320 --> 08:22.560
Man Di.

08:22.640 --> 08:23.560
Man Di.

08:24.480 --> 08:25.320
Yuanqing,

08:25.840 --> 08:26.760
lead the troops to attack the city now.

08:29.920 --> 08:30.800
Man Di.

08:31.440 --> 08:32.360
Man Di.

08:36.799 --> 08:37.720
Man Di.

08:38.799 --> 08:40.240
-Man Di!
-Man Di!

08:41.080 --> 08:41.919
Man Di!

08:42.919 --> 08:45.160
Man Di!

08:45.240 --> 08:46.520
Man Di!

08:47.960 --> 08:49.280
You little whelp of the Xie family,

08:49.360 --> 08:51.200
did you really think you could win?

08:51.280 --> 08:52.640
Look at the smoke signals behind me.

08:54.040 --> 08:56.920
The Chongzhou forces
have already breached Lucheng.

08:57.440 --> 09:00.040
Today, let's see where you run.

09:02.240 --> 09:03.360
Xie Wu.

09:04.280 --> 09:06.040
-Stay behind and protect Changyu.
-Yes, sir.

09:07.080 --> 09:08.160
Hyah!

09:08.240 --> 09:10.800
You little Xie brat,
where do you think you're going?

09:24.680 --> 09:26.080
Now that's strange.

09:26.600 --> 09:28.280
A lowly soldier like you
dares to stand in my way?

09:28.360 --> 09:30.520
Killing an old rebel like you?

09:30.600 --> 09:31.800
I alone am enough!

09:31.880 --> 09:33.600
Arrogant child.

09:33.680 --> 09:35.800
When I was leading armies
and slaughtering enemies,

09:36.440 --> 09:38.040
you were still playing in the mud.

09:53.880 --> 09:54.720
Good lad.

09:54.800 --> 09:57.120
Following that Xie whelp
is a waste of your talent.

09:57.880 --> 09:59.280
Why not come with me instead?

10:01.360 --> 10:03.280
In this life, my name is Xie.

10:03.360 --> 10:04.400
Not "dog".

10:04.480 --> 10:05.920
You ungrateful wretch.

10:17.600 --> 10:20.080
You're skilled with a short blade,
yet your strikes are heavy and powerful.

10:20.160 --> 10:22.240
Use less brute force. Go with the flow.

10:47.080 --> 10:48.800
On the battlefield,

10:48.880 --> 10:51.560
an enemy's attacks shift in an instant.

10:53.080 --> 10:55.560
Predictable patterns are easily read.

10:55.640 --> 10:57.560
Once they see through you,
you lose your composure.

11:08.600 --> 11:12.120
‎Charge!

11:27.760 --> 11:30.360
You think these little tricks can beat me?

11:31.840 --> 11:33.120
Kill me.

11:34.640 --> 11:36.000
Make it quick.

11:38.320 --> 11:40.160
Tie him up. Take him back.

11:40.240 --> 11:41.160
Yes.

11:54.960 --> 11:56.680
What is He Jingyuan to you?

11:57.440 --> 11:59.640
He's the commander of our Jizhou army.

12:01.360 --> 12:02.800
This blade technique of yours,

12:02.880 --> 12:05.360
it was created by the two tiger generals
of the Wei clan back in the day.

12:05.440 --> 12:07.600
But Wei Qilin is already dead.

12:07.680 --> 12:09.840
Only He Jingyuan still knows it.

12:09.920 --> 12:11.920
How did you come
to inherit his true teachings?

12:12.520 --> 12:14.600
You know the sworn brother of General He?

12:14.680 --> 12:17.920
The great traitor Wei Qilin,
who doesn't know him?

12:18.000 --> 12:19.280
Who hasn't heard of him?

12:33.240 --> 12:34.760
Once I've taken you captive,

12:34.840 --> 12:36.520
while He Jingyuan's
still clinging to life,

12:36.600 --> 12:38.400
I'll negotiate a deal with him.

13:16.480 --> 13:19.760
Please, send troops
to rescue them immediately.

13:44.760 --> 13:47.320
SUI

13:49.400 --> 13:53.760
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

13:59.920 --> 14:01.160
Such a fine young lady…

14:02.480 --> 14:04.000
How did you get so badly hurt?

14:12.640 --> 14:14.520
I didn't mean to hide who I was.

14:16.320 --> 14:17.360
Are you…

14:18.640 --> 14:19.480
angry?

14:25.360 --> 14:26.600
Back at the military camp,

14:26.680 --> 14:28.680
I knew your identity wasn't simple.

14:29.720 --> 14:30.880
But I never imagined

14:31.480 --> 14:33.440
you were the most noble Grand Princess…

14:35.920 --> 14:37.200
and that you would treat my wounds.

14:40.160 --> 14:42.680
I used to think my status was noble,

14:43.320 --> 14:45.240
that marrying for the country

14:45.760 --> 14:47.720
would be the greatest sacrifice
of my life.

14:48.920 --> 14:50.960
But only after coming
to the battlefield did I realize,

14:51.760 --> 14:53.400
what is a Grand Princess, really?

14:57.760 --> 14:59.240
Today, killing the rebel prince,

14:59.960 --> 15:01.840
that honor was earned by your own hands.

15:01.920 --> 15:03.520
With Prince Changxin dead,

15:04.240 --> 15:05.880
both court and people will be shocked.

15:06.480 --> 15:08.840
Your name will be remembered
by everyone in Dayin,

15:09.440 --> 15:10.720
recorded by the historians.

15:20.760 --> 15:21.680
I bow to you

15:22.760 --> 15:23.800
as the Grand Princess

15:25.320 --> 15:26.320
and as myself, Qi Shu, with gratitude.

15:28.880 --> 15:30.920
Changyu. Rest well.

15:36.000 --> 15:37.040
I used to think…

15:38.480 --> 15:39.720
that as long as I had a kind heart…

15:41.920 --> 15:43.840
I could protect those around me.

15:48.400 --> 15:50.800
But only after parting
in life and death did I realize…

15:53.240 --> 15:54.520
my soft mercy

15:54.600 --> 15:57.360
only pushes more people
into desperate straits.

15:57.440 --> 16:00.280
-Sister!
-I'm here.

16:00.360 --> 16:01.640
-I'm here.
-Big Brother.

16:01.720 --> 16:02.800
I'm here.

16:04.000 --> 16:05.400
Look how brave I was.

16:05.480 --> 16:08.680
I didn't…I didn't flinch.

16:15.040 --> 16:17.960
Man Di!

16:21.120 --> 16:22.800
Adoptive Father was right.

16:24.280 --> 16:25.600
On the battlefield,

16:26.240 --> 16:28.360
you fight or you die.

16:29.040 --> 16:29.880
General He.

16:29.960 --> 16:31.760
General He is on the tower.

16:32.360 --> 16:33.400
Hurry.

16:46.360 --> 16:48.720
General, we've won.

16:50.760 --> 16:51.600
General.

16:57.720 --> 16:58.560
General.

17:04.520 --> 17:05.599
General.

17:11.800 --> 17:13.599
General!

17:14.640 --> 17:16.200
General!

17:17.839 --> 17:19.640
If I had known this earlier…

17:20.560 --> 17:23.040
If I had killed Prince Changxin sooner…

17:25.560 --> 17:27.800
General He and the others wouldn't have…

17:31.600 --> 17:33.040
General He's death…

17:34.280 --> 17:35.760
is not your fault.

17:40.920 --> 17:42.160
Changyu.

17:43.720 --> 17:45.120
He was like you.

17:48.480 --> 17:50.520
Both of you fought
to protect your own land.

17:51.560 --> 17:54.600
Your Highness, Miss Fan,
Commander Li requests an audience.

17:59.800 --> 18:00.720
Come in.

18:01.360 --> 18:02.280
Changyu,

18:03.480 --> 18:04.800
rest well.

18:05.440 --> 18:06.360
I'll take my leave now.

18:15.920 --> 18:17.120
Commander Li,

18:18.440 --> 18:19.560
you're all heroes.

18:21.640 --> 18:22.480
Rest and recover well.

18:44.160 --> 18:45.000
Commander Li.

18:45.080 --> 18:47.120
Commander Fan played the heroic stunt.

18:48.440 --> 18:50.080
Finally got what you wanted.

18:53.760 --> 18:55.960
You were too badly wounded at the time.

18:57.160 --> 18:58.120
I knocked you out…

18:59.360 --> 19:00.600
because I was afraid you'd play the hero

19:01.160 --> 19:03.240
and throw your life away for nothing.

19:03.320 --> 19:05.800
I'd rather have died
outside the city walls that day

19:06.920 --> 19:09.080
than be knocked out

19:09.160 --> 19:12.120
and have everyone tell me
the battle was over.

19:13.960 --> 19:15.280
To have no chance at all

19:16.000 --> 19:17.040
to avenge my master,

19:18.760 --> 19:20.640
just living on, a complete joke.

19:21.680 --> 19:23.640
If the prized student General He trained

19:24.560 --> 19:26.800
had died senselessly out of pride,

19:28.080 --> 19:29.520
that would have been the real joke.

19:43.480 --> 19:44.680
I came this time…

19:47.280 --> 19:49.320
to fulfill my master's final wish.

19:54.200 --> 19:55.360
TO BROTHER HE

19:56.160 --> 19:57.960
From now on, there's no need
for us to meet again.

20:33.720 --> 20:35.240
"Brother He…"

20:35.320 --> 20:36.200
"The Chan…"

20:39.560 --> 20:42.160
"And… live…10,000…"

20:42.240 --> 20:46.880
"I've survived until now
only thanks to Brother He's help.

20:47.840 --> 20:52.440
My sole wish was to reveal the truth
for countless innocent souls of Jinzhou.

20:53.320 --> 20:56.240
Now that the Chancellor
has issued another kill order."

20:58.440 --> 21:00.960
And here, someone "cannot continue living,

21:01.480 --> 21:04.680
nor do I wish to make
things difficult for Brother He."

21:05.800 --> 21:06.880
QILIN

21:06.960 --> 21:09.080
Qilin cannot continue living,

21:10.000 --> 21:12.160
nor do I wish to make
things difficult for Brother He.

21:12.680 --> 21:14.960
My wife and I
will end our lives ourselves.

21:16.400 --> 21:19.880
That we have lived an extra 16 years

21:20.760 --> 21:22.440
is already great fortune.

21:22.520 --> 21:25.880
"I beg Brother He,
please protect the lives

21:26.720 --> 21:28.480
of our two young daughters."

21:29.600 --> 21:30.440
Sister.

21:32.000 --> 21:33.160
Sister.

21:35.640 --> 21:36.720
Dan,

21:36.800 --> 21:39.200
pretend you never saw this letter today.

21:39.800 --> 21:41.080
Don't tell anyone.

21:43.640 --> 21:44.560
Leave the letter here.

21:44.640 --> 21:46.040
You can go back now.

21:46.760 --> 21:47.880
Got it, Sister.

21:55.640 --> 21:58.040
You know the sworn brother of General He?

21:58.120 --> 22:01.360
The great traitor Wei Qilin,
who doesn't know him?

22:01.440 --> 22:02.680
Who hasn't heard of him?

22:04.720 --> 22:09.240
"The great traitor, Wei Qili.

22:09.320 --> 22:13.280
Held the grain, with no delivery.

22:13.880 --> 22:17.720
Doomed a hundred thousand souls to end."

22:17.800 --> 22:18.960
My father is Wei…

22:21.480 --> 22:22.600
Wei Qilin?

22:23.400 --> 22:25.080
The great traitor Wei Qilin?

22:25.160 --> 22:26.160
No.

22:27.360 --> 22:28.200
No.

22:28.280 --> 22:30.920
If my father were a traitor
who harmed the country,

22:31.000 --> 22:34.000
how could my mother ever forgive him?

22:36.680 --> 22:39.240
But what really happened?

22:41.120 --> 22:45.880
Crown Prince Chengde
and General Xie Linshan

22:45.960 --> 22:47.840
guarded the border,

22:47.920 --> 22:50.080
fighting bloody battles
on the battlefield.

22:50.160 --> 22:53.720
The great traitor Wei Qilin
colluded with the Northern Jue,

22:53.800 --> 22:55.920
preventing the army's grain from arriving.

22:56.000 --> 23:01.720
A hundred thousand soldiers
starved for five days and five nights.

23:01.800 --> 23:05.840
The great traitor Wei Qilin,
who doesn't know him?

23:05.920 --> 23:08.040
Who hasn't heard of him?

23:08.120 --> 23:12.560
"The great traitor, Wei Qilin.

23:12.640 --> 23:17.240
Held the grain, with no delivery.

23:17.320 --> 23:21.400
Doomed a hundred thousand souls to end.

23:21.480 --> 23:25.360
Jinzhou's tragedy, soldiers' pain.

23:25.440 --> 23:29.640
Starved the prince till death's domain.

23:29.720 --> 23:30.560
-General…"
-Fan Changyu!

23:32.880 --> 23:35.200
Stop. Come here.

23:44.200 --> 23:45.240
Have you figured out why?

23:47.040 --> 23:47.880
Mother,

23:47.960 --> 23:52.200
I won't play
the "great traitor" game anymore.

23:54.560 --> 23:55.640
Good girl, Changyu.

23:58.880 --> 24:00.160
In this world,

24:01.720 --> 24:02.800
how many people

24:03.480 --> 24:06.800
can truly tell loyalty from treachery,
right from wrong?

24:06.880 --> 24:11.240
"The great traitor, Wei Qilin."

24:20.360 --> 24:21.280
Not true.

24:22.680 --> 24:23.840
Father isn't a traitor.

24:27.400 --> 24:28.560
It's not like that.

24:30.080 --> 24:31.360
It's not like that.

24:31.440 --> 24:32.920
It's not true!

24:39.160 --> 24:40.160
It's me.

24:50.840 --> 24:51.800
Does it hurt?

24:57.280 --> 24:58.320
Sui Yuanqing…

25:00.680 --> 25:01.640
Is he dead?

25:04.640 --> 25:05.480
He got away.

25:05.560 --> 25:08.600
Your Highness, I'm here to save you.
Quick, take the heir and leave.

25:10.600 --> 25:11.720
Hyah!

25:14.400 --> 25:15.440
Let's go.

25:35.320 --> 25:36.880
He'll die sooner or later.

25:39.360 --> 25:41.800
I'll bring his head back to Lin'an

25:41.880 --> 25:43.600
and offer it in sacrifice
to fellow villagers.

25:47.360 --> 25:48.480
Okay.

25:49.480 --> 25:50.560
Does it hurt a lot?

25:53.160 --> 25:54.200
Just a flesh wound.

25:57.800 --> 25:59.720
How is General Wu?

26:00.320 --> 26:01.680
His shoulder bone was broken.

26:01.760 --> 26:03.160
But luckily, he's strong.

26:03.680 --> 26:04.840
No danger to his life.

26:05.640 --> 26:08.360
It's just, he might never
be able to lift a blade again.

26:10.760 --> 26:12.480
He did it all to protect me.

26:15.280 --> 26:17.680
Twice on the battlefield,
he risked his life to save me.

26:20.000 --> 26:21.600
He's my lifesaver.

26:22.360 --> 26:23.480
Today,

26:23.560 --> 26:26.360
if he hadn't blocked that spear
from Prince Changxin,

26:26.440 --> 26:27.480
I'd be dead.

26:30.920 --> 26:31.960
In this world,

26:33.240 --> 26:35.000
no one has the right to make you die.

26:42.760 --> 26:44.400
I've been having nightmares all night.

26:45.400 --> 26:47.640
In my dreams, it's either Man Di's face…

26:49.600 --> 26:51.560
or the faces of the soldiers.

26:51.640 --> 26:54.840
They die in my dreams,
over and over again.

26:58.120 --> 26:59.440
And every time…

27:01.680 --> 27:03.800
Every time, I can't save them.

27:17.440 --> 27:19.800
Was the Battle of Jinzhou 17 years ago…

27:21.480 --> 27:23.280
this brutal as well?

27:25.360 --> 27:26.480
The Battle of Jinzhou…

27:28.720 --> 27:29.760
was even worse.

27:31.600 --> 27:32.640
Seventeen years ago,

27:33.240 --> 27:35.480
my father fought
the Northern Jue army for months.

27:36.400 --> 27:39.520
But because the grain never arrived,
reinforcements never came,

27:39.600 --> 27:41.960
his men, too exhausted
to resist, lost the battle.

27:42.800 --> 27:44.480
The Northern Jue swept through.

27:44.560 --> 27:47.000
Hundreds of thousands of lives
were treated like dirt.

27:47.080 --> 27:50.440
My father was hung from the city wall.

27:57.960 --> 27:59.040
Then…

27:59.760 --> 28:01.680
then the one who transported
the grain back then,

28:03.320 --> 28:04.440
Wei Qilin,

28:05.280 --> 28:06.520
did he really…

28:08.600 --> 28:10.160
cause the deaths of so many people?

28:12.920 --> 28:15.520
Could there be another truth hidden?

28:16.720 --> 28:17.800
Wei Qilin,

28:18.640 --> 28:21.760
back then, he was Wei Yan's
most trusted right-hand man.

28:23.080 --> 28:25.040
He also fought alongside my father.

28:25.960 --> 28:27.320
He was a man of loyalty and honor.

28:27.920 --> 28:28.840
But later…

28:31.280 --> 28:35.040
in the eyes of the Yanzhou army,
he became the greatest traitor of Dayin.

28:38.680 --> 28:41.320
Why do you suddenly ask about this?

28:42.440 --> 28:45.120
Fan Changyu, say it.

28:46.400 --> 28:48.920
Telling him the truth is the right thing.

28:50.000 --> 28:52.840
Even if he turns against you
because of it, that’s what is right.

28:53.920 --> 28:54.960
Say it.

28:55.680 --> 28:56.520
Changyu.

28:58.360 --> 28:59.240
I wanted to ask.

29:02.080 --> 29:04.480
When will General He's funeral be held?

29:07.600 --> 29:08.560
Six days from now.

29:09.280 --> 29:12.560
General He's seventh-day rite will be held
together with my father's commemoration.

29:15.800 --> 29:19.280
It's almost fated, you could say.

29:20.640 --> 29:22.040
On this very day 17 years ago,

29:23.160 --> 29:24.760
my father fell in battle at Jinzhou.

29:25.520 --> 29:28.320
Every year at this time,
the generals of the Xie family,

29:29.560 --> 29:32.960
no matter where they are,
return to pay respects to my father.

29:34.200 --> 29:35.560
Then, when the time comes,

29:36.960 --> 29:39.080
I'd also like to offer incense
to General Xie.

29:39.760 --> 29:40.760
May I?

29:43.160 --> 29:44.000
Sure.

29:51.960 --> 29:56.120
FUNERAL CORTEGE OF HE JINGYUAN
LOYAL AND UPRIGHT GENERAL OF DAYIN

29:56.200 --> 29:59.800
VIRTUE COMMANDS LOYALTY

29:59.880 --> 30:01.480
MEMORIAL OFFERING

30:01.560 --> 30:02.400
Wenkan,

30:03.120 --> 30:05.280
you've followed me

30:05.360 --> 30:06.960
since you were a child.

30:07.560 --> 30:10.320
You are my most accomplished student.

30:11.760 --> 30:15.040
The reason I kept you by my side

30:15.120 --> 30:18.440
is because the court is treacherous,
full of shifting tides.

30:18.520 --> 30:20.320
Li and Wei play with power.

30:21.960 --> 30:24.440
I didn't want you to be seduced by them,

30:24.520 --> 30:27.680
to become a pawn
in someone else's schemes.

30:29.000 --> 30:30.560
What I hope for

30:31.080 --> 30:33.560
is a pure servant of Dayin.

30:38.040 --> 30:41.280
And one more thing, the Fan sisters.

30:41.960 --> 30:43.080
After I'm gone,

30:43.840 --> 30:47.120
I hope you will treat them with sincerity.

30:47.200 --> 30:52.640
Only then can I rest in peace.

30:57.560 --> 30:59.920
Commander Li, this is a funeral banner
sent by Chancellor Wei.

31:01.640 --> 31:04.080
LOYAL NAME REACHES THE SUN
NOBLE SPIRIT COMMANDS AWE

31:04.160 --> 31:05.240
Commander Li,

31:05.800 --> 31:07.640
this is a funeral banner
sent by Grand Tutor Li.

31:08.800 --> 31:11.280
BLOOD-BATHED SPIRITS
ETERNAL IN THE ANNALS

31:12.520 --> 31:15.240
Sir, which one shall we hang?

31:30.840 --> 31:33.840
So you've decided to help the Grand Tutor
go against the Wei faction?

31:55.680 --> 31:58.320
Huai'an will surely carry on
my teacher's will.

31:59.520 --> 32:01.600
I will not let down the soldiers
and people of Dayin who gave their lives.

32:08.440 --> 32:10.800
INK-WASHING PAVILION

32:43.040 --> 32:43.920
Cousin,

32:44.440 --> 32:45.520
please.

32:52.440 --> 32:55.200
LIU WAN'ER, DAUGHTER OF A CONCUBINE FROM A
BRANCH FAMILY RELATED TO PRINCESS CHANGXIN

32:58.320 --> 32:59.440
Mother said…

33:00.480 --> 33:03.240
said Cousin's injuries aren't light.

33:03.760 --> 33:05.200
These tonics help…

33:05.880 --> 33:07.880
help wounds heal.

33:08.640 --> 33:11.880
She also said… said Father has confirmed,

33:11.960 --> 33:13.960
the Marquis of Wu'an
isn't paying attention to this place.

33:14.720 --> 33:15.920
She asks Cousin to rest here…

33:17.840 --> 33:18.920
and recover peacefully.

33:26.640 --> 33:28.280
Why are you shaking so much?

33:29.400 --> 33:30.360
Afraid of your cousin?

33:49.520 --> 33:50.240
Cousin…

33:54.560 --> 33:55.680
Careful. It's hot.

34:02.160 --> 34:03.200
Bland food does not suit me.

34:04.200 --> 34:05.400
How about you

34:06.320 --> 34:07.440
drink it for me?

34:09.239 --> 34:10.120
I…

34:15.560 --> 34:16.520
Cousin,

34:17.239 --> 34:18.440
you need to flee.

34:19.320 --> 34:22.159
Father heard that the Marquis of Wu'an
is coming to capture you personally.

34:22.679 --> 34:25.520
He's afraid that after the city falls,
our entire family will be executed.

34:26.120 --> 34:27.480
He already put poison in the soup.

34:28.120 --> 34:30.520
Said he'd take your head to surrender.

34:30.600 --> 34:31.600
I'm sorry…

34:32.639 --> 34:34.080
I didn't want to harm you.

34:38.199 --> 34:40.159
Thank you for telling me.

35:11.680 --> 35:13.400
Father.

35:14.040 --> 35:14.920
Mother.

35:17.160 --> 35:19.720
Why did you kill my parents?

35:20.520 --> 35:23.480
With your skills, you could have escaped.

35:23.560 --> 35:26.320
You could have just run away.

35:26.400 --> 35:28.640
Why did you have to kill them?

35:29.600 --> 35:32.000
They were going to take
my head to surrender.

35:32.720 --> 35:34.200
Why shouldn't I kill them?

35:40.920 --> 35:42.480
They're not worth your tears.

35:43.800 --> 35:45.880
In their hearts,
you were never that important.

35:47.000 --> 35:50.560
Otherwise, they wouldn't have sent you
to bring me that poisoned soup.

35:52.560 --> 35:53.600
Now…

35:55.120 --> 35:56.040
you're free.

36:22.200 --> 36:24.680
Cousin, take me with you.

36:24.760 --> 36:26.280
My family is all dead.

36:26.360 --> 36:28.440
I don't know where I should go anymore.

36:30.960 --> 36:33.000
I killed your whole family,

36:33.080 --> 36:34.800
and you still want to come with me?

36:34.880 --> 36:36.800
I'm begging you.

36:36.880 --> 36:38.920
Take me with you. Please?

36:44.560 --> 36:46.760
What a lovely, delicate flower you are.

36:48.400 --> 36:50.360
But why is it that some flowers, like you,

36:50.880 --> 36:52.600
can only cling and depend,

36:53.880 --> 36:55.080
unable to live a moment

36:55.680 --> 36:57.000
without someone to hold onto,

36:58.640 --> 36:59.840
while others

37:00.400 --> 37:02.360
grow on their own,

37:03.560 --> 37:04.960
covered in thorns,

37:05.800 --> 37:08.680
making people both love and hate them?

38:42.440 --> 38:45.320
Master, last night, the heir
slaughtered the entire Liu family.

38:47.960 --> 38:49.040
So what if he did?

38:49.560 --> 38:50.880
Nothing to make a fuss about.

38:52.080 --> 38:54.080
-Where is he?
-In the study.

38:57.440 --> 38:58.280
Yuanqing.

38:59.680 --> 39:01.680
-Yuanqing.
-Brother.

39:02.200 --> 39:03.320
I finally found you.

39:05.280 --> 39:07.880
How are you? How is Mother?

39:12.120 --> 39:13.040
Brother.

39:14.400 --> 39:15.680
Am I really…

39:16.680 --> 39:18.120
really not as good as Xie Zheng?

39:19.000 --> 39:20.440
Is that why I lost one after another?

39:21.080 --> 39:22.520
Is that why I got Father killed?

39:25.280 --> 39:26.320
In my heart,

39:27.040 --> 39:30.120
you are the most
formidable person in this world.

39:31.320 --> 39:34.040
That Xie Zheng just got lucky
and won a few battles.

39:34.880 --> 39:36.280
But our cause isn't lost yet.

39:36.880 --> 39:38.200
We still have a chance.

39:39.240 --> 39:40.360
The cause?

39:42.520 --> 39:43.880
Empty and illusory.

39:45.000 --> 39:47.480
Ever since the late king misled my father,

39:47.560 --> 39:49.280
he's been chasing some grand cause.

39:49.360 --> 39:50.480
And in the end?

39:50.560 --> 39:51.600
Nothing but emptiness.

39:52.840 --> 39:54.560
I don't believe in any damn cause.

39:54.640 --> 39:56.440
What do I care who is at the throne?

39:59.120 --> 40:02.400
How can we, the Sui family,
just give up like this?

40:03.000 --> 40:05.960
Xie Zheng has all the advantages,
timing, position, and support.

40:06.720 --> 40:08.480
Are you too afraid to revenge against him?

40:09.440 --> 40:10.920
Though my body is weak,

40:11.640 --> 40:14.960
I'll still fight to my last breath
in the death battle with them.

40:15.040 --> 40:16.240
What about you?

40:16.840 --> 40:18.680
A true man walks between heaven and earth.

40:19.280 --> 40:20.840
How can you live on without even fighting?

40:21.600 --> 40:24.720
If you can't win, then that's fate.

40:26.920 --> 40:29.440
But today, you're like rotten mud.

40:29.520 --> 40:31.960
Is this how you honor Father's soul?

40:32.800 --> 40:35.960
Do you even know who killed him?

40:38.120 --> 40:39.200
Not Xie Zheng?

40:39.280 --> 40:42.160
It was Fan Changyu.

40:46.200 --> 40:47.480
Fan Changyu.

40:50.520 --> 40:51.400
Fan Changyu!

40:52.880 --> 40:53.920
Her again.

40:54.000 --> 40:55.280
That pig-slaughtering woman.

40:55.880 --> 40:57.680
How dare she?

40:59.960 --> 41:00.800
Brother,

41:00.880 --> 41:02.000
I want revenge!

41:05.360 --> 41:06.520
Go ahead.

41:06.600 --> 41:08.520
Whatever you do, I support you.

41:09.440 --> 41:10.800
Mother will be in my care along the way.

41:10.880 --> 41:12.320
You just go kill Fan Changyu,

41:12.920 --> 41:14.760
to honor Father's spirit in heaven.

44:05.360 --> 44:08.520
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

44:08.600 --> 44:09.480
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song
